description: Come taste the differenceWelcome to Mad Mouth Gyro and Mediterranean Catering. Based out of Cleveland, Ohio in the center of Avon's historic shopping and arts district.  Every dish is made to order and created using only the freshest and finest ingredients. We serve only the finest meats, freshest bread and vegetables, and desserts that are baked fresh daily. Our authentic menu transports you to city streets of Greece, and only the finest authentic ingredients from the area are used.
name: Mad Mouth Gyro
